2. **Fix RLS on `group_members`** — profile join is commented out in `useGroupMembers.ts`; all display names are `null`. Restore the join once RLS recursion bug is fixed.
3. **Read real role from DB** — `page.tsx` + `info/page.tsx` infer role from `created_by`. Replace with actual `group_members.role` query after RLS fix.
4. **`comments.parent_id UUID → comments.id`** — reply threading UI is built; FK column must exist.
