6. **`UNIQUE(group_share_id, user_id, type)` on reactions** — rapid taps create duplicate rows. Add constraint + use `ON CONFLICT DO NOTHING` in `useDropEngagement.ts`.
7. **Index `group_shares(group_id, shared_at DESC)`** — feed cursor pagination degrades without it.

